Modifications by SwapDK add optional `memo` support to
`WalletAccountBtc.sendTransaction` / `signTransaction`, emitting the memo
bytes as an additional OP_RETURN output on the spending transaction.
Required for THORChain / MAYAChain inbound observation, which routes on
the OP_RETURN payload of the BTC deposit.

Specific modifications are noted in the changed files via header
comments. The intent is to upstream these changes — see the package
README for the PR tracking link.
